item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Christina Milian - It's About Time (Japan Edition) / 2x Shakira
item.description:
Hello, I am searching for these 2 songs below from Shakira. They both belong to Japan Version of an early album of hers "Pies Descalzos". If anybody has them, may you please share?

Shakira - Estoy aquí (The Love & House Mix) 8:31 - Japan bonus track of Pies Descalzos
Shakira - Estoy aquí (Radio edit) 4:40 - Japan bonus track of Pies Descalzos

Also, I've been looking everywhere but didn't succeed at finding a lossless version of Christina Milian - It's about time (Japan Edition) which has some extra tracks and some different version of songs included in the standard edition (e.g: L.O.V.E. (RedOne Remix).

Thanks in advance
item.author: Marin
